outperforms other trackers in terms of average overlap accuracy (A) and expected average overlap (EAO). ↑ stands for the higher the best,

with the minimum area bounding box. Ref stands for the refinement step in Subsection 3.3. minABoxAngle stands for the orientation of 
the minimum area bounding box. ellipseAngle stands for the orientation of the best fitting ellipse. The result shows that the effectiveness 
of ellipse orientation and refinement step significantly improve the performance of SiamMask.
